OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1782857894
OL,3,CGermany crash out on penalties to
OL,4,CParaguay in historic World Cup upset
OL,6,FFour-time World Cup winners Germany
OL,7,Fhave crashed out of the tournament
OL,8,Fafter they were beaten on penalties
OL,9,Ffor the first time ever by underdogs
OL,10,FParaguay, following a 1-1 draw in
OL,11,FBoston.
OL,13,FThe South American side's fans were
OL,14,Fleft in tears of disbelief and joy
OL,15,Ffollowing one of the greatest upsets
OL,16,Fin recent memory.
OL,18,FThe Germans had never previously lost
OL,19,Fa shootout in the tournament.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
