FL,318,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31702
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1782857894
OL,3,CGermany crash out on penalties to
OL,4,CParaguay in historic World Cup upset
OL,6,FBut that record was ended
OL,7,Fsensationally by Paraguay, who
OL,8,Fdefended for 120 minutes before
OL,9,Foutstanding central defender Jose
OL,10,FCanale hit the winning penalty in
OL,11,Fsudden death.
OL,13,F"The feeling is hard to explain,"
OL,14,FParaguay defender Gomez said. "I'm
OL,15,Fvery proud of my team-mates, of the
OL,16,Fgroup."
OL,18,F"I'm most impressed by our unity. We
OL,19,Fhave incredible strength to face any
OL,20,Fsituation. Germany knew they needed to
OL,21,Fwork incredibly hard to beat us."
OL,26,@uD@AOUuD@aO]vD@_OUzD@AOU}D@aO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/10
