PN,31704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1782857894
OL,3,CGermany crash out on penalties to
OL,4,CParaguay in historic World Cup upset
OL,6,FAt that stage it looked like Germany
OL,7,Fwould go on to win but it was not to
OL,8,Fbe.
OL,10,FSubscribe for free to our weekly
OL,11,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,12,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,13,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,15,FThey were furious after a contentious
OL,16,FVAR decision disallowed an extra-time
OL,17,Fheader from defender Jonathan Tah, the
OL,18,Fofficials ruling Waldemar Anton had
OL,19,Ffouled keeper Orlando Gill.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
