PN,31705
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1782857894
OL,3,CGermany crash out on penalties to
OL,4,CParaguay in historic World Cup upset
OL,6,FBayern Munich defender Tah would go on
OL,7,Fto miss the crucial penalty, skying
OL,8,Fover the bar and allowing Canale to
OL,9,Fwin it 4-3 in the tie-breaker.
OL,11,FGermany were badly frustrated by a
OL,12,Fside that sat back and left little
OL,13,Fspace for them to play.
OL,15,FIt made for a match that offered
OL,16,Flittle spectacle, in which the main
OL,17,Ftalking point was a courageous and
OL,18,Fhighly-disciplined defensive display
OL,19,Fby Paraguay.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
