PN,31706
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1782857894
OL,3,CGermany crash out on penalties to
OL,4,CParaguay in historic World Cup upset
OL,6,FCentral defensive pair Gustavo Gomez
OL,7,Fand Canale in particular gave a
OL,8,Fmemorable performance as Nagelsmann's
OL,9,Fside were left with no answers and
OL,10,Fwere forced to accept their fate would
OL,11,Fbe settled from 12 yards.
OL,13,FParaguay stunned Germany four minutes
OL,14,Fbefore half-time.
OL,16,FA clever piece of overlap play down
OL,17,Fthe right saw Matias Galarza released
OL,18,Fdown the outside of defender Nathaniel
OL,19,FBrown.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
