PN,31707
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1782857894
OL,3,CGermany crash out on penalties to
OL,4,CParaguay in historic World Cup upset
OL,6,FGalarza crossed into the six-yard box
OL,7,Fwhere Enciso had been left entirely
OL,8,Funmarked to nod the ball into the
OL,9,Fground and in past the static Manuel
OL,10,FNeuer.
OL,12,FGermany finally rallied before the
OL,13,Fbreak and threatened through Felix
OL,14,FNmecha, his shot from Leroy Sane's tee-
OL,15,Fup was deflected just beyond the far
OL,16,Fpost. His team had 79 per cent
OL,17,Fpossession in the first half but
OL,18,Falmost nothing to show for it in front
OL,19,Fof goal.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
