PN,31708
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1782857894
OL,3,CGermany crash out on penalties to
OL,4,CParaguay in historic World Cup upset
OL,6,FEnciso almost doubled his team's lead
OL,7,Fafter Paraguay made a confident start
OL,8,Fto the second half, only a good spread
OL,9,Ffrom Neuer preventing the forward from
OL,10,Fslotting in at the near post.
OL,12,FHe was made to regret not taking his
OL,13,Fchance as within minutes Germany were
OL,14,Flevel. Florian Wirtz sent over a deep
OL,15,Fcross form the left, Havertz got
OL,16,Facross his defender and flicked a deft
OL,17,Fheader into the far corner to earn his
OL,18,Fteam a reprieve.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
