PN,31709
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1782857894
OL,3,CGermany crash out on penalties to
OL,4,CParaguay in historic World Cup upset
OL,6,FTah thought he had given his side the
OL,7,Flead via a thumping header from a
OL,8,Fcorner, but was denied after VAR
OL,9,Fadjudged goalkeeper Orlando Gill to
OL,10,Fhave been fouled, and penalties
OL,11,Fbeckoned.
OL,13,FHavertz and Newcastle's Nick Woltemade
OL,14,Fboth missed for Germany, Antonio
OL,15,FSanabria and Fabian Balbuena blew two
OL,16,Fmatch-winning efforts, before Tah
OL,17,Fmissed the target and Canale settled
OL,18,Fit.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
