PN,31710
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1782857894
OL,3,CGermany crash out on penalties to
OL,4,CParaguay in historic World Cup upset
OL,6,FArsenal's German forward Havertz said:
OL,7,F"I'm a little lost for words. This is
OL,8,Fmy second World Cup and both times it
OL,9,Fcame to nothing. All I can do is
OL,10,Fapologise.
OL,12,F"We have to take a hard look at
OL,13,Fourselves, especially the players, and
OL,14,FI'm leaving the coach out of that."
